name: Kubu Indah Guest House
address: Batumadeg, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: Awesome place to stay. The rooms are clean and really comfortable. The area is quiet. Plus, the breakfast taste delicious! 10/10.
review 2: Amazing location and beautiful people, The oner is a legend,he help us with everything, they have also a Shop in front of the villa, they rent scooters, there are very good warungs around and the place it's very close to kilinking beach
review 3: Love the stay here in Kubu indah ‚ù§Ô∏èneat and clean rooms and plus breakfast, with good distance to kiliking beach
review 4: Great hotel, very clean and quiet. Staff was great and welcoming. The place is far from beaches or tourist attractions which is great if you want some relaxing time away in the mountains.
review 5:
Central location to explore the island. Wonderful kind staff. Breakfast is delicious and they accommodate dietary requirements.
The rooms are beautiful, clean and air conditioned. The bed is comfy. Handy shop at the front and lots of Warung options.
We would return without hesitation.

name: Warung Nengah Mesin
address: Batumadeg, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: I had a delightful experience at this restaurant. The food was excellent, and the staff provided exceptional service. We ordered two coffees and two servings of fried rice, and we were not disappointed. Everything was delicious! Visiting for breakfast, I was charmed by the sight of chickens crossing the street, adding to the pleasant ambiance. Additionally, the restaurant offers free wifi, which we used to plan out our route for today's adventure. I highly recommend this place for a satisfying meal, a unique atmosphere, and convenient amenities.
review 2:

review 3: The best food I had during my trip in Indonesia. It was closed of my homestay then I went 3 times. The food is fresh cooked and the family is lovely. The food is typical from the country. The prices are really low for the quality of the meals. I really recommand to stop there if you're staying in the island.
review 4: One of the best place I have been eat in Bali !! Everything is fresh. Gado-gado, nasi campur, curry,... all delicious !
review 5:
When I ordered the coconut, I didn't wait for them to bring it fresh.  Mixed smoothie bowl was top delicious, even the food brilliant.
Is worth waiting 30-60min for your food.
